'''巴伊特体育场''' ({{Lang-ar|استاد البيت}} ''[[阿拉伯語羅馬化|羅馬化:]] Āstād āl-Bayt'')位于[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]][[豪爾_(卡達)|豪爾]]，是一座可伸縮天幕的體育場，將承辦[[2022年國際足總世界盃|2022年國際足總世界盃]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arabianbusiness.com/revealed--firms-behind-construction-qatar-s-world-cup-stadiums-602613.html#.VcxR9PlVikp|title=Revealed: The firms behind the construction Qatar's World Cup stadiums|publisher=Arabian Business|author=Neha Bhatia|date=13 August 2015|accessdate=13 August 2015|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709183006/https://www.arabianbusiness.com/revealed--firms-behind-construction-qatar-s-world-cup-stadiums-602613.html#.VcxR9PlVikp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
卡塔尔[[2018年和2022年国际足联世界杯申办过程|竞争2022年世界杯足球赛主办权]]时，申办方案中的12座球场就包含一座位于[[豪爾_(卡達)|豪爾]]的“豪爾体育场”。按照这一方案，豪尔体育场世界杯期间可容纳45,330名观众，世界杯后保留25,500个永久座椅，高层看台的19,830个模块式座椅将被拆除；体育场的造型模仿贝壳，顶棚可以弯曲。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2010-12-13/08184974837.shtml |title=揭秘2022世界杯12大体育场:总投资570亿(图) |date=2010-12-13 |work=新浪 |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205082525/http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2010-12-13/08184974837.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>赢得主办权后，卡塔尔将12座体育场减为8座<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://epaper.southcn.com/nfdaily/html/2018-07/14/content_7737883.htm |title=南方日报记者探访2022年卡塔尔世界杯筹备情况——“从最大到最小，我们2022见” |date=2018-07-14 |publisher=南方日报 |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205081555/http://epaper.southcn.com/nfdaily/html/2018-07/14/content_7737883.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。八座体育场之一仍然建在豪爾。2014年6月卡塔尔发布了位于豪尔的体育场的正式设计方案。新方案将世界杯期间的观众容量增加到6万，世界杯后观众容量减至3.2万人；体育场外形改为模仿[[贝都因人|贝都因人]]传统的帐篷，体育场也因之命名为巴伊特体育场。<ref name="new_design">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2014/06/new_design_stadium_disguised_as_a_tent |title=New design: Stadium disguised as a tent |date=2014-06-22 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2018-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011103540/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2014/06/new_design_stadium_disguised_as_a_tent |dead-url=no }}</ref>

巴伊特体育场计划在2020年底完工。2022年世界杯足球赛的开幕式将在巴伊特体育场举行{{noteTag|早期的方案把世界杯开幕式和决赛都安排在[[卢塞尔体育场|卢塞尔体育场]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.goal.com/en/news/2022-fifa-world-cup-qatar-lusail-design-launch-qatar/9tfz49pmnqg119yqgi7p2w31h |title=2022 FIFA World Cup: Qatar unveils design for Lusail stadium |date=2018-12-16 |work=Goal.com |accessdate=2020-12-05 |language=en |archive-date=2019-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422135339/https://www.goal.com/en/news/2022-fifa-world-cup-qatar-lusail-design-launch-qatar/9tfz49pmnqg119yqgi7p2w31h |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年7月发布的正式版赛程将开幕式改在巴伊特体育场<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/fifa-world-cuptm-match-schedule-confirmed-hosts-qatar-to-kick-off-2022-tournamen |title=FIFA World Cup™ match schedule confirmed: hosts Qatar to kick off 2022 tournament at Al Bayt Stadium |date=2020-07-15 |work=FIFA.com |accessdate=2020-12-05 |language=en-GB |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205083706/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/fifa-world-cuptm-match-schedule-confirmed-hosts-qatar-to-kick-off-2022-tournamen |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。此外，巴伊特体育场将承办自世界杯小组赛至半决赛的比赛。世界杯后，体育场的上层看台将被拆除，球场将成为豪尔当地俱乐部[[艾哥爾體育會|艾哥爾體育會]]的主场。<ref name="asFacts ">{{Cite news |url=https://en.as.com/en/2020/11/24/football/1606208635_491873.html |title=Facts about Al-Bayt stadium, the inaugural venue at Qatar 2022 |date=2020-11-24 |work=as |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130103617/https://en.as.com/en/2020/11/24/football/1606208635_491873.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 建筑 ==
巴伊特体育场的造型模仿卡塔尔沙漠游牧民的帐篷。外立面的黑色条纹和体育场内部的图案也模仿了帐篷的纹饰。顶棚可以开合。体育场内装有空调。<ref name="design">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-bayt-stadium/design |title=Al Bayt Stadium Design |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927223808/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-bayt-stadium/design |dead-url=no }}</ref>

世界杯后，巴伊特体育场上层看台的座椅将被拆除并捐赠<ref name="Legacy">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-bayt-stadium/legacy |title=Al Bayt Stadium Legacy |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927194100/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/al-bayt-stadium/legacy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="fifa-sustainability" />。体育场的包厢层将改建为五星级酒店，体育场内将开设购物中心、餐厅、健身房和多功能厅。<ref name="fifa-sustainability" />此外，体育场内还将开设运动医学中心。<ref name="Legacy" />体育场外围已建成公园、跑道、自行车道、游乐场、咖啡厅、餐馆。<ref name="fifa-sustainability" />

2020年，巴伊特体育场获得{{le|全球可持续性评估体系|Global Sustainability Assessment System}}五星级认证，成为卡塔尔世界杯第二座获五星级认证的球场。<ref name="fifa-sustainability ">{{Cite news |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/al-bayt-stadium-achieves-outstanding-sustainability-rating |title=Al Bayt Stadium achieves outstanding sustainability rating |last=FIFA.com |date=2020-07-27 |work=FIFA.com |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en-GB |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101070155/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/al-bayt-stadium-achieves-outstanding-sustainability-rating |dead-url=no }}</ref>

